<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="ATA80">
<l>cerukkiṉāl veṟpeṭutta vettaṉaiyō tiṇṭō</l>
<l>ḷarakkaṉaiyu muṉṉiṉ ṟaṭartta - tiruttakka</l>
<l>mālayaṉuṅ kāṇā taraṟṟi makiḻntēttak</l>
<l>kālaṉaiyum veṉṟutaitta kāl</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>They stood  in front [and] pressed down the Rakṣasa,</l>
<l>with how many firm arms that lifted the mountain out of pride,</l>
<l>the feet that had victoriously kicked Death, while Māl, fit for Śrī,</l> 
<l>and the Unborn one did not see [him], wept, rejoiced [and] praised.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
